{"tid":616596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想買二手PS4送弟弟　美青年被黑人賣家槍殺","createTime":"2018-04-04T09:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T12:39:00.000Z","uid":14065,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"edf1b72aefddeb42a43ae69c1b99da248b0bc4ee","tid":616596,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:51:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180404/1328269/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180404%2F1328269%2F&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaSwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=1be39a2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180404%2F1328269%2F&h=94aeb47d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180404/1328269/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180404/640_3bddeb08410f22b3f4d817fbb18d9c62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180404%2F640_3bddeb08410f22b3f4d817fbb18d9c62.jpg&h=c187b8f7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國紐澤西州一名20歲青年想買二手PS4送給弟弟，他上網找到賣家後，和對方約定面交，沒想到卻遭賣家搶劫、虐待，最後被開槍射殺。 <br />\n<br />\n檢察官說，20歲的狄亞茲－戴爾加多（Danny Diaz-Delgado）在網路上找二手遊戲系統，要買來送給他其中一個弟弟。他找到一位PS4賣家後，和對方相約3月23日在翠登市（Trenton）東區面交。狄亞茲－戴爾加多出門之後，就再也沒回家。 <br />\n<br />\n默瑟郡（Mercer County）檢察官辦公室表示，在一條河的岸邊發現狄亞茲－戴爾加多的屍體，他的頭部、軀幹和腿部被射中多槍。警方逮捕了嫌犯湯普森（Rufus Thompson），根據宣誓書內容，檢察官稱，湯普森用粉紅色膠帶和黑色電線將狄亞茲－戴爾加多綁起來，並槍殺他。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，狄亞茲－戴爾加多從銀行領錢後就和賣家見面，沒想到卻被對方綁架，還被帶到樹林裡虐待，要求他交出更多錢。警方消息來源向媒體透露，嫌犯運用酷刑手段，逼迫狄亞茲－戴爾加多交出簽帳金融卡密碼。警方在湯普森家裡找到一個空的PS4外盒、一卷粉紅色膠帶，和一部電線被剪斷的電視機，湯普森周一出庭時否認控罪。 <br />\n<br />\n（盧宥竹／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"989841d386f797f42e9cc6a02c209423ff3a3068","tid":616596,"uid":11695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179a37a9b251c188e286e79b8b3cd337052a92fc","tid":616596,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f08d72af56407d7539cdd080d4bb0f71c039ad4","tid":616596,"uid":21664,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:58:25.000Z","msg":"黑奴"},{"pid":"29d6eaece90ceef05149ec15a2b148049ef9156e","tid":616596,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d324144bfbed1cae23e7137c88724b8ac3bea9","tid":616596,"uid":11148,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"力架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9a719052ceb3390cb40dfd742a49025fffa0e9","tid":616596,"uid":63870,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T10:00:51.000Z","msg":"為個少少錢殺人，好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac533edb1db54361dcaa85157b26b6a65fa237e8","tid":616596,"uid":41508,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T10:01:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b55aed560d1a5fb558f1fe1a2a1617d2c8c6b21","tid":616596,"uid":41974,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T10:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.hktvmall.com/h0888001/84777/h0888001_10017931_170308042319_01_1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.hktvmall.com%2Fh0888001%2F84777%2Fh0888001_10017931_170308042319_01_1200.jpg&h=060ed1ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d26d5d5afbe82b6574495a677a11